  <title>Organization and Concision</title>

  <objectives>
    <title>Learning Objectives</title>
    <ul>
      <li><p>Organize information within sentences effectively</p></li>
      <li><p>Move from known to new information</p></li>
      <li><p>Eliminate wordiness and redundancy</p></li>
      <li><p>Use active constructions for concision</p></li>
      <li><p>Revise for economy without sacrificing clarity</p></li>
      <li><p>Cohesion</p></li>
      <li><p>Coherence</p></li>
      <li><p>Given-new contract</p></li>
      <li><p>End-focus</p></li>
      <li><p>Wordiness</p></li>
